Text: "A curious girl from a small city falls deeply depressed after 2 long years\
  \ of not fitting in with a\u013Al of the routines she made. She set's out on a brave\
  \ tale to experience the world, she lands herself in portugal where she meets local\
  \ peace-makers. They help to show her the pathway to deep inner healing. She falls\
  \ in love with her-self, finds her happiness, and peacefulness. She falls in love."
